						               													<description>Xeno-Force pits mankind&amp;rsquo;s finest marines against alien threats in a scenario driven fast play skirmish game. &amp;#10;Battle your way past tough alien horrors to complete your mission. &amp;#10;Play games in your favourite sci-fi universe with this flexible and detailed system. &amp;#10;Xeno-Force is a scenario driven game. It is about using your games to tell interesting stories and building those stories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This unique semi-cooperative game means you and your friends work together in a team against a single alien opponent to accomplish your objectives, but also compete to gain the most glory and honour.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Jump straight into the action with pre-generated characters and scenarios, or play as a longer campaign game, linking missions together to develop your own engaging story.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Xeno-Force rulebook includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Detailed but straight forward game rules with lots of examples&amp;#10;     Three introductory scenarios with more on the website&amp;#10;     Full campaign and character development and advancement rules&amp;#10;     Six difference character classes with unique combat styles&amp;#10;     Tons of weapons, equipment and abilities&amp;#10;     Nine Xenotypes ( &amp;ldquo;Bugs&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Cyborgs&amp;rdquo; etc.); pick one that suits your model collection&amp;#10;     Rules for vehicles&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Full Advancement Rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Xeno-Force allows you to advance your characters from mission to mission using a very thorough and detailed advancement system. Watch your characters grow in strength and develop through campaigns. Specialise them in different styles of combat so each one can become genuinely unique.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use for RPGs:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Xeno-Force works really well to support RPG games to run tactical missions when the players &amp;quot;call in the cavalry&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Full Support:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The game is fully supported online, with missions and aliens published on the website.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Community:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Please join in the community and share your experiences, questions and scenarios. The more players who join in the better.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
